msgid ""
"This guide explains how to integrate link:https://github.com/smallrye/smallrye-jwt/[SmallRye JWT] into your Quarkus application to implement link:https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc7519[JSON Web Token (JWT)] security in compliance with the MicroProfile JWT specification.\n"
"Youâll learn how to verify JWTs, represent them as MicroProfile JWT `org.eclipse.microprofile.jwt.JsonWebToken`, and secure Quarkus HTTP endpoints using bearer token authorization and link:https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Role-based_access_control[Role-Based Access Control]."
msgstr "Este guia explica como integrar link:https://github.com/smallrye/smallrye-jwt/[o SmallRye JWT] ao seu aplicativo Quarkus para implementar a seguranĂ§a link:https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc7519[do JSON Web Token (JWT)] em conformidade com a especificaĂ§ĂŁo MicroProfile JWT. O senhor aprenderĂĄ a verificar os JWTs, representĂĄ-los como MicroProfile JWT `org.eclipse.microprofile.jwt.JsonWebToken` e proteger os pontos de extremidade HTTP do Quarkus usando autorizaĂ§ĂŁo de token de portador e link:https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Role-based_access_control[controle de acesso baseado em funĂ§ĂŁo] ."

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/security-jwt.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
